        Frontend Developer.<br>
        Co-developed EventSphere — contributed to the platform design, UI/UX, feature ideation, and overall project vision.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; margin-bottom:22px;">
        <a href="mailto:tanishkotian3101@gmail.com" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.88rem; transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#EA4335'" onmouseout="this.style.color=''">
